title: Patio, Night Patrol, Wheelchair Accessible, Pool, Gym, Lounge
posting_body: ['Discover modern touches, comfort, and convenience at Renew Park Viva!', 'Located off of I-80 in the heart of Solano County, the community provides easy access to Napa, San Francisco, and the Sacramento region.', 'Renew Park Viva sits just minutes away from Travis Air Force Base, Solano County Westfield Mall, and everything that Fairfield has to offer.', 'Each renovated home features quartz countertops, stainless steel appliances, built-in microwaves, and private patio and balconies.', 'Walk-in closets and washers and dryers are available in select homes.', 'Residents are invited to relax poolside, enjoy the community lounge and BBQ area, play a round of tennis, or work out in the state-of-the-art fitness facility.', 'Renew Park Viva is a pet-friendly community, welcoming both cats and dogs with a few breed restrictions.', '-Heat', '-Accepts Electronic Payments', '-Controlled Access', '-Night Patrol', '-On-site Management', '-Disposal', '-On-site Maintenance', '-Refrigerator', '-Wheelchair Accessible', '-Private Balcony', '-Air Conditioner', '-Individual Climate Control', 'Call Now or Text', 'show contact info', 'to contact our team.', 'For more information, visit us at: <URL>']
